{
  "texts": [
    "They employed both TF-IDF Word2Vec for feature extraction, finding that TF-IDF yielded better results compared to Word2Vec embeddings.",
    "The study implemented various models, including SVM, RF, AdaBoost, and KNN.",
    "Among these, SVM was found to outperform the other models in terms of accuracy.",
    "In their study, Akuma et al. [1] analyzed a dataset of HS and offensive language from kagglefoot_2 using four ML-based algorithms: KNN, DT, LR, and NB, along with two distinct word embeddings, BoW and TF-IDF.",
    "Their work showed that DT when integrated with TF-IDF achieved the best accuracy score of 0.92 when compared to the other models in their research."
  ]
}